<!DOCTYPE html>
<html style="                   width:300px;">
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <title>巴哈公會文章篩選器</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>巴哈公會文章篩選器 1.0.0</h2>
    <hr>
    <h3>篩選文章</h3>
    <h4>(對插件右鍵點選"選項"進行設定)</h4>
    <input id="readmore" value="看更多" style="width:120px;height:40px;border:3px red double;"

type="button"> <input id="filter" value="篩選文章" style="width:120px;height:40px;border:2px black solid;"

type="button"><br>
    <br>
    <input id="autoClosePic" name="autoClosePic" value="autoClosePic" type="checkbox">
    <label>自動關圖</label> <input id="filter_type_forbidden" name="filter_type_forbidden"

      value="filter_type_forbidden" type="checkbox"> <label>過濾內文</label><br>
    <br>
    <input name="filter_type" id="filter_type_search" type="radio">搜尋特定ID <input

      name="filter_type" id="filter_type_black" type="radio">排除黑名單ID <input name="filter_type"

      id="filter_type_none" type="radio">關閉
    <hr>
    <h3>便捷工具</h3>
    <input id="good" value="推全部文章" style="width:120px;height:40px;border:2px blue dashed;"

type="button"> <input id="bad" value="噓全部文章" style="width:120px;height:40px;border:2px red dashed;"

type="button"> <br>
    <br>
    <input id="hide_intro" name="hide_intro" value="hide_intro" type="checkbox">
    <label>隱藏公會介紹</label><br>
    <br>
    <input id="hide_announcement" name="hide_announcement" value="hide_announcement"

      type="checkbox"> <label>隱藏公告</label> <br>
    <br>
    <input id="hide_management" name="hide_management" value="hide_management" type="checkbox"><label>
      隱藏幹部列表</label>
    <script src="popup.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
